frames.caption: A large, realistic dinosaur animatronic is displayed in a spacious industrial warehouse. Several people are operating the animatronic, which features exposed mechanical components and a lifelike appearance. The dinosaur's mouth is wide open, showcasing its detailed teeth and tongue.
frames.description: The scene is set in a large industrial warehouse, where a team is working on a life-sized dinosaur animatronic. The environment is spacious and well-lit, with high ceilings and large windows.

frames.caption: A large animatronic dinosaur roars menacingly inside a spacious industrial warehouse. The creature's mouth is wide open, revealing sharp teeth, as it stands amidst a cloud of dust on the concrete floor.
frames.description: The scene is set in a large, well-lit industrial warehouse, where a life-sized animatronic dinosaur is positioned as if in mid-roar. The atmosphere is intense and dramatic, with the dinosaur's presence dominating the space.

frames.caption: A large, mechanical dinosaur stands menacingly in an industrial warehouse. Its massive frame is accentuated by metal components and tubes, suggesting a fusion of organic and mechanical elements. Dust swirls around its feet, adding to the dramatic atmosphere.
frames.description: The scene takes place in a spacious industrial warehouse, where a hybrid dinosaur, part machine and part creature, dominates the space. The environment is gritty and filled with dust, creating a tense and dramatic setting.
